title: Percentage
name: NOTE 1%3A
definition: Required for services other than FGC and FGD w hen the ACT field is "N" and the WST field is not populated.
fieldNotes: Required when the first position of the REQTYP field is "S", "E", "V", "X" or "W" and the ACT field is "C", "M", "T" or "R".
Prohibited when the ACT field is "D".
